kpi.name: M1034C43

kpi_info.title: E-DCH ALLO REJECT MAX USERS PER OPER
kpi_info.use: The number of times when the E-DCH uplink transport channel cannot be selected in this cell due to maximum amount of E-DCH users in the cell or in the local cell group. UPDATED: When the E-DCH cannot be selected as the uplink transport channel in this cell because the number of E-DCH users in the cell would exceed the limit defined by MaxNumberEDCHCell or the number of E-DCH users in local cell group would exceed MaxNumberEDCHLCG

kpi.kpi_alias: E-DCH ALLO REJECT MAX USERS PER OPER
